text: Ismailovo () is a rural locality (a village) in Kakrybashevsky Selsoviet, Tuymazinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 197 as of 2010. There are 28 streets. == Geography == It is located 3 km from Tuymazy, 1 km from Kakrybashevo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Tuymazinsky District
title: Ismailovo, Tuymazinsky District, Republic of Bashkortostan
